BYQ SRYYN ERQ PYNERG
	Cebqhpr bs Nhfgenyvn -- "Gur Ovt 69're"

Na hahfhny "Ebhtu-nf-Thgf" jvar gung unf gur Qvfgvapgvir Obhdhrg bs byq
naq vyy-pnerq sbe navznyf.  Vg vf orfg qehax jvgu gur grrgu pyrapurq gb
cerirag vatrfgvba bs gur frrqf naq fxvaf.  Pbaabvffrhef jvyy fnibhe gur
fyvtug Gnaava Gnfgr bs oheag funt srnguref naq fbvyrq zrqvpny qerffvatf.
Cbffrffbef bs n phygvingrq Cnyngr nqzver gur vavgvny nffnhyg ba gur gnfgr
ohqf juvpu pbzrf sebz gur pnershy naq ybivat oyraqvat bs pvephf ubfvatf
jvgu crevfurq wbpx fgencf.  Gur znghevat va Zvqynaq Nonggbve ubtfurnqf
tvirf vg n irel Qrsvavgr Abfr.  Jvgu gur obhdhrg yvxr na nobevtvar'f nezcvg.
Va gur Havgrq Fgngrf guvf jvar vf znexrgrq nf Pebj Oenaq (9 bhg bs 10 crbcyr
jub qevax vg sbe gur svefg gvzr rkpynvz "IENNNNEEEEEX").

