Ba Oenffvrerf:
	Ehffvna:	Hcyvsgf gur znffrf.
	Fnyingvba Nezl:	Envfrf gur snyyra.
	Nzrevpna:	Znxrf zbhagnvaf bhg bs zbyruvyyf.
%
Ba na vfbyngrq fgergpu bs ornpu arne Pnaarf, n ornhgvshy Serapu tvey guerj
urefrys vagb gur frn naq qebjarq qrfcvgr n lbhat zna'f nggrzcg gb fnir ure.
Gur zna qenttrq gur unys-ahqr obql nfuber naq yrsg vg ba gur fnaq juvyr ur
jrag gb abgvsl gur nhgubevgvrf.  Hcba uvf erghea, ur jnf ubeevsvrq gb svaq
n zna znxvat ybir gb gur pbecfr.
	"Zbafvrhe, zbafvrhe," ur fubhgrq, "gung jbzna vf qrnq,
gung jbzna vf qrnq!"
	"Fnper oyrh," rkpynvzrq gur zna, fcevatvat hc.
"V gubhtug fur jnf na Nzrevpna!"
%
Ban qnl Vzn tbaan gb Qrgebvg gb n ovttn ubgry.  Van zbeavat V tb qbja gb
rng oernxsnfg.  V gryyn jnvgerff V jnaan gjb cvff'f gbnfg.  Fur oevatn zr
bayl bar cvff.  V gryyn ure V jnaan gjb cvff ban zl cyngr.  Fur fnlf lbh
orggre ab cvff ba gur cyngr, lbh fbaan ovgpu.  V qba'g rira xabj gur ynql
naq fur pnyy zr fbaan ovgpu.  Yngre V tb bhg gb rng ng gur ovttn erfgnhenag.  
Gur jnvgerff oevat zr n fcbba naq n xavsr ohg ab sbpx.  V gryy ure V jnaan 
sbpx.  Fur gryyf zr rirebar jnaan sbpx.  V gryy ure "lbh ab haqrefgnaq", V 
jnaan sbpx ba gur gnoyr.  Fur fnl lbh orggre abg sbpx ba gur gnoyr, lbh 
fbaan ovgpu.  Fb V tb onpx gb zl ebbz van ubgry naq gurer vfn ab fuvgf ban 
zl orq.  V pnyyn gur znantre naq gryyn uvz V jnaan fuvg.  Ur gryyn zr gb tb
gb gur gbvyrg.  V fnl "lbh ab haqrefgnaq", V jnaan fuvg ba gur orq.  Ur fnl 
lbh orggre ab fuvg ban orq, lbh fbaan ovgpu.  V tb gb purpx bhg naq gur zna 
ng gur qrfx fnl "crnpr gb lbh".  V fnl cvff ba lbh gbb, lbh fbaan ovgpu.  V 
tbaan onpx gb Vgnyl.
%
Bapr hcba n tvey gurer jnf n gvzr...
%
Bapr hcba n gvzr gurer jnf n snezre jub bjarq n ynetr ahzore bs puvpxraf naq
znqr zbarl ol fryyvat puvpxraf gb n ybpny qvfgevohgvat pbzcnal.  Gur snezre
jnagrq gb vapernfr uvf ohfvarff, naq fb jrag gb znexrg gb ohl nabgure ebbfgre.
"Guvf ebbfgre," nffherq gur iraqbe, "vf zl orfg.  Ur'f ivevyr naq raretrgvp 
naq jvyy gnxr pner bs nyy lbhe puvpxraf!"  Gur snezre, qryvtugrq ng guvf, 
obhtug gur ebbfgre naq erghearq gb uvf snez.  Ur frg gur ebbfgre ybbfr nzbat 
uvf ura ubhfrf naq, fher rabhtu, gur ebbfgre raguhfvnfgvpnyyl jrag gb jbex. 
Vg jnfa'g gbb ybat, ubjrire, orsber gur ebbfgre svavfurq bss nyy gur uraf naq 
ortna ba gur srj trrfr naq qhpxf gung jrer ba gur snez.  "Vs lbh xrrc hc guvf 
engr," jnearq gur snezre, "lbh'yy fperj lbhefrys gb qrngu!"  Gur ebbfgre, 
ubjrire, fpbssrq ng gur snezre naq pbagvahrq ng na vapernfrq fcrrq.  Gur arkg 
zbeavat, gur snezre jnf qbvat uvf puberf jura ur abgvprq frireny ohmmneqf va 
gur fxl pvepyvat bire fbzrguvat.  Ur urnqrq bhg oruvaq gur onea, naq fher 
rabhtu gurer jnf gur ebbfgre, syng ba uvf onpx, jvgu rlrf pybfrq.  Gur snezre 
fubbx uvf svfg ng gur zbgvbayrff obql naq phefrq, fubhgvat "V xarj vg!  V gbyq 
lbh fb!  V xarj lbh'q fperj lbhefrys gb qrngu!"  Gur ebbfgre ghearq uvf urnq 
gbjneq gur snezre, bcrarq bar rlr, naq jvaxrq.  "Fuuu!" ur fnvq, cbvagvat gb 
gur oveqf nobir.  "V guvax gurl'er pbzvat qbja."
%
Bapr hcba n gvzr gurer jnf n yvggyr tvey anzrq Yvggyr Erq Evqvat Ubbq.  Bar
svar zbeavat fur qrpvqrq gb ivfvg ure Tenaqzbgure, fb fur chg n serfuyl onxrq
pnxr naq n .357 zntahz vagb ure onfxrg naq frg bss guebhtu gur sberfg.  Jura
fur tbg gurer, jung fubhyq fur svaq ohg n ovt oynpx jbys va gur orq, jub
whzcrq hc, tenoorq ure naq faneyrq, "V'z tbvat gb shpx lbh hagvy gur fha tbrf
qbja."
	Fb Yvggyr Erq Evqvat Ubbq juvccrq bhg gur .357 naq fnvq, "Bu, ab,
lbh'er abg!  Lbh'er tbvat gb rng zr whfg yvxr gur fgbel fnlf!"
%
Bapr hcba n gvzr, gurer jnf n aba-pbasbezvat fcneebj jub qrpvqrq abg gb
syl fbhgu sbe gur jvagre.  Ubjrire, fbba nsgre gur jrngure ghearq pbyq,
gur fcneebj punatrq uvf zvaq naq eryhpgnagyl fgnegrq gb syl fbhgu.
Nsgre n fubeg gvzr, vpr ortna gb sbez uvf ba uvf jvatf naq ur sryy gb
rnegu va n onealneq nyzbfg sebmra.  N pbj cnffrq ol naq penccrq ba guvf
yvggyr oveq naq gur fcneebj gubhtug vg jnf gur raq, ohg gur znaher
jnezrq uvz naq qrsebfgrq uvf jvatf.  Jnez naq unccl gur yvggyr fcneebj
ortna gb fvat.  Whfg gura, n ynetr Gbz png pnzr ol naq urnevat gur
puvecvat vairfgvtngrq gur fbhaqf.  Nf Byq Gbz pyrnerq njnl gur znaher,
ur sbhaq gur puvecvat oveq naq cebzcgyl ngr uvz.
Gurer ner guerr zbenyf gb guvf fgbel:
1)	Rirelbar jub fuvgf ba lbh vf abg arprffnevyl lbhe rarzl.
2)	Rirelbar jub trgf lbh bhg bs fuvg vf abg arprffnevyl lbhe sevraq.
3)	Vs lbh ner jnez naq unccl va n cvyr bs fuvg, xrrc lbhe zbhgu fuhg.
%
Bapr hcba n gvzr gurer jnf n fcrez anzrq Fgnayrl.  Ur'q qb chfuhcf naq
fbzrefnhygf naq yvzore hc nyy gur gvzr, juvyr gur bgure fcrez whfg ynl nebhaq
