Gung ur erprvirq n cnepry ol cbfg,
	Vg pbagnvarq, fb jr urneq,
	N zntavsvprag gheq,
Naq gur onyyf bs uvf tenaqsngure'f tubfg.
%
N znevar orvat frag gb Ubat Xbat
Tbg n qbpgbe gb nygre uvf qbat.
	Ur fnvyrq bss jvgu n gbby
	Syng naq guva nf n ehyr -
Jura ur tbg gurer ur sbhaq ur jnf jebat.
%
N zngurzngvpvna anzrq Unyy
Unq n urkurqebavpny onyy,
	Naq gur fdhner bs vgf jrvtug
	Gvzrf uvf crpxre'f, cyhf rvtug,
Jnf sbhe-svsguf bs svir-rvtuguf bs shpx-nyy.
%
N zngurzngvpvna anzrq Unyy
Unf n urknurqebavpny onyy,
	Naq gur phor bs vgf jrvtug
	Gvzrf uvf crpxre'f, cyhf rvtug
Vf uvf cubar ahzore -- tvir uvz n pnyy...
%
N zvqqyr-ntrq pbqtre anzrq Oehva
Sbhaq uvf ybir yvsr pbzcyrgryl va ehva,
	Sbe ur syvegrq jvgu syvegf
	Jrnevat cnagf naq ab fxvegf,
Naq ur arire tbg va sbe ab fperjva'.
%
N zvyxznvq gurer jnf, jvgu n fghggre,
Jub jnf ybaryl naq jnagrq n shggre.
	Fur unq abjurer gb ghea,
	Fb fur qvqqyrq n puhea,
Naq znantrq gb pbzr jvgu gur ohggre.
%
N zbegvpvna jub cenpgvfrq va Svsr
Znqr ybir gb gur pbecfr bs uvf jvsr.
	"Ubj pbhyq V xabj, Whqtr?
	Fur jnf pbyq, qvq abg ohqtr--
Whfg gur fnzr nf fur'q npgrq va yvsr."
%
N areibhf lbhat sryybj anzrq Serq
Gbbx n punezvat lbhat jvqbj gb orq.
	Jura ur'q qvqqyrq n juvyr
	Fur erznexrq jvgu n fzvyr,
"Lbh'ir tbg vg nyy va ohg gur urnq."
%
N arjyljrq pbhcyr sebz Tbfura
Fcrag gurve ubarlzbba fnvyvat gur bprna.
	Va gjragl-rvtug qnlf
	Gurl tbg ynvq rvtugl jnlf --
Vzntvar fhpu shpxvat qribgvba!
%
N arjyl-jrq zna bs Creh
Sbhaq uvzfrys va n greevoyr fgrj:
	Uvf jvsr jnf va orq
	Zhpu qrnqre guna qrnq,
Naq fb ur unq ab bar gb fperj.
%
N abgbevbhf juber anzrq Zf. Urnefg,
Va gur cyrnfherf bs zra jnf jryy-irefrq.
	Ernqf gur fvta b're gur urnq
	Bs ure jryy-ehzcyrq orq
"Gur phfgbzre nyjnlf pbzrf svefg."
%
N ahqvfg erfbeg ng Oranerf
Gbbx n zvqtrg va nyy hanjnerf.
	Ohg ur znqr zrzoref jrrc
	Sbe ur whfg pbhyqa'g xrrc
Uvf abfr bhg bs cevingr nssnvef.
%
N cnffvbangr erq-unverq tvey
Jura lbh xvffrq ure, ure frafrf jbhyq juvey,
	Naq ure gjng jbhyq trg jrg,
	Naq jbhyq jvttyr naq serg,
Naq ure phag-yvcf jbhyq phey naq hashey.
%
N crghynag zna bapr fnvq, "Cvfu,
Lbhe phag vf nf ovt nf n qvfu."
	Fur ercyvrq, "Jul, lbh sbby,
	Jvgu lbhe yvzc yvggyr gbby,
Vg'f yvxr qevivat n cva jvgu n svfu."
%
N cvbhf byq jbzna anzrq Gjrnx
Unq gnhtug ure intvan gb fcrnx.
	Vg jnf serdhragyl yvnoyr
	Gb dhbgr sebz gur Ovoyr,
Ohg jura shpxvat -- abg rira n fdhrnx!
%
N cvbhf lbhat ynql anzrq Svaartna
Jbhyq pnhgvba ure sevraq, "Jryy, lbh'er va ntnva;
	Fb gvzr vg nevtug,
	Znxr vg ynfg guebhtu gur avtug,
Sbe V pregnvayl qba'g jnag gb fva ntnva!"
%
N cvbhf lbhat ynql bs Puvpurfgre
Znqr nyy bs gur fnvagf va gurve avpurf fgve
	Naq rnpu zbeavat ng zngva
	Ure oernfg va cvax fngva
Znqr gur ovfubc bs Puvpurfgre'f oerrpurf fgve.
%
N cyhzore jubfr anzr jnf Wbua Oevax
Cyhzorq gur pbbx nf fur orag b're gur fvax.
	Ure erfvfgnapr jnf fgbhg,
	Naq Wbua Oevax crgrerq bhg,
Jvgu uvf cvcr-jerapu nyy yvzore naq cvax.
%
N cbggre jub yvirq va Obzonl
Bapr snfuvbarq n phag bhg bs pynl;
	Ohg gur urng bs uvf cevpx
	Xvyarq gur qnza guvat gb oevpx
Naq punsrq nyy uvf sberfxva njnl.
%
N cerggl jvsr yvivat va Gbhef
Qrznaqrq ure qnvyl nzbhe.
	Ohg gur uhfonaq fnvq, "Ab!
	Vg'f gb zhpu.  Yrg vg tb!
Zl onpxfvqrf ner qenttvat gur sybbe."
%
N cerggl lbhat ynql anzrq Ibtry
Bapr fng urefrys qbja ba n zbyruvyy.
	N phevbhf zbyr
	Abfrq vagb ure ubyr --
Zf. Ibtry'f bx, ohg gur zbyr'f vyy.
%
N cerggl lbhat znvqra sebz Senapr
Qrpvqrq fur'q "whfg gnxr n punapr."
	Fur yrg urefrys tb
	Sbe na ubhe be fb
Naq abj nyy ure fvfgref ner nhagf.
%
N encghebhf lbhat sryyngevk
Bar qnl jnf ng jbex ba svir cevpxf.
	Jvgu na haubyl pel
	Fur juvccrq bhg ure tynff rlr:
"Gryy gur oblf V pna abj gnxr ba fvk."
%
N erpxyrff lbhat ynql bs Senapr
Unq ab dhnyzf nobhg gnxvat n punapr,
	Ohg fur gubhtug vg jnf pehqr
	Gb trg fperjrq va gur ahqr,
Fb fur nyjnlf jrag ubzr jvgu qnzc cnagf.
%
N erznexnoyr enpr ner gur Crefvnaf;
Gurl unir fhpu crphyvne qvirefvbaf.
	Gurl znxr ybir gur jubyr qnl
	Va gur hfhny jnl
Naq fnir hc gur avtugf sbe creirefvbaf.
%
N ebznagvp nggenpgvba unf pyhat
Gb n punc bs jubz qnzfryf unir fhat:
	"'Gvf gur Fpbhetr sebz gur Rnfg,
	Gung ynfpvivbhf ornfg
