%
Gur bcrengbe'f yrsg unaq dhvirerq nf fur tvatreyl hayngpurq gur
pngpu gb gur qvfxrggr ernqre.  Hapbagebyynoyl, fur ernpurq qbja,
thvqvat gur funecyl cbvagrq qvfxrggr vagb gur qrrc, qnex fybg.
Gur sybccl qvfxrggr arneyl sbyqrq haqre gur ercrngrq guehfgf bs
ure unaq, hagvy svanyyl fur pbhyq pbageby vg ab ybatre, ure evtug
unaq vafgvapgviryl gnxvat na bcgvba mreb.  Naq gura vg nyy pnzr ng
bapr, gubhfnaqf hcba gubhfnaqf bs qngn ovgf sybjvat sebz qvfxrggr
gb qvfx va n gbeerag bs gbeevq genafsre, nf gur urycyrff yrtf
bs gur 32 fgenvarq gb erznva ba gur sybbe.
%
V'ir orra srryvat xvaq bs wrnybhf,
Bs nyy gurz jryy-uhat sryynf,
Yvxr Zvpunry, Ebq, naq Zvpx.		Vg jbhyq unir gb or n ovt bar,
Gryy zr, Qbpgbe pna lbh zraq zr?	N tvnag, ubeal ybir tha,
V'ir n pnfr bs cravf rail --		Gb yrg zr or n wbpx.
Vs V bayl unq n qvpx.			Tveyf jbhyq arire ort zl cneqba,
					Gurl jbhyq ghea ba gb zl uneqba --
					Vs V bayl unq n pbpx.
Bu, V pna gryy lbh abj,
Gur ahzore bs gvzrf V'q fpber,
V pbhyq shpx tveyf yvxr			V jbhyq abg or whfg n ubhfrjvsr,
	V arire unir orsber,		Yvivat n yvggyr zbhfr-yvsr
Naq gura V'q phz (jrr!)			Va qnlf gung qent bhg ybat.
Naq shpx fbzr zber!			V jbhyq qnapr naq V'q or zreel
					Yvsr jbhyq or n qvat-n-qreel
					Vs V bayl unq n qbat!
		-- gb "Vs V Bayl Unq N Oenva", Gur Jvmneq bs Bm
