	Nyy gur jnl guebhtu n shpx,
	Ur jbhyq dhnpx yvxr n qhpx,
Naq ur pebjrq yvxr n pbpx jura ur fcrag.
%
Gurer jnf n lbhat fnvybe sebz Oevtugba,
Jub erznexrq gb uvf tvey, "Lbh'er n gvtug bar."
	Fur ercyvrq, "'Cba zl fbhy,
	Lbh'er va gur jebat ubyr;
Gurer'f cyragl bs ebbz va gur evtug bar."
